<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#efefeb">Noah Ararat 
<font size="13">The Wise Prince, Age 12</font></font></b></font>

2
00:00:19,270 --> 00:00:22,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is something bothering you, um...</font>

3
00:00:22,950 --> 00:00:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name is Gigi.</font>

4
00:00:24,790 --> 00:00:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gigi?</font>

5
00:00:26,240 --> 00:00:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, u-um...</font>

6
00:00:29,290 --> 00:00:31,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The line of people bringing 
you birthday gifts</font>

7
00:00:32,230 --> 00:00:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">still hasn't ended.
It's been three days...</font>

8
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's about right.</font>

9
00:00:39,320 --> 00:00:42,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It lasted a full week last year.</font>

10
00:00:42,120 --> 00:00:43,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-A <i>week</i>?!</font>

11
00:00:46,410 --> 00:00:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't just receive them 
and be done with it.</font>

12
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The item received and its sender 
need to be recorded in detail.</font>

13
00:00:52,800 --> 00:00:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's quite time-consuming.</font>

14
00:00:55,700 --> 00:00:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm sure Evelyn will take 
care of everything just fine.</font>

15
00:01:00,650 --> 00:01:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gigi, you're on the job.</font>

16
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:04,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Right!</font>

17
00:01:06,420 --> 00:01:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Prince Noah, now twelve years old,</i></font>

18
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>has been recognized for fully mastering 
the magic sword Leviathan.</i></font>

19
00:01:14,810 --> 00:01:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}By direct imperial order, he is stationed
at the Ministry of Military Affairs,</i></font>

20
00:01:15,170 --> 00:01:18,840
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15"><font color="#f3ede6">Ministry of Military Affairs</font></font></font></b></font>

21
00:01:18,850 --> 00:01:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}which presides over the imperial army.</i></font>

22
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:26,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And serving as its minister is...</i></font>

23
00:01:28,470 --> 00:01:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Noah.</font>

24
00:01:29,850 --> 00:01:31,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good. Enter.</font>

25
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:43,660
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#efefeb">Henry Ararat 
<font size="13">Minister-Prince of Military Affairs, Fourth Prince</font></font></b></font>

26
00:01:40,940 --> 00:01:44,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you are, Noah. I've been waiting.</font>

27
00:01:44,420 --> 00:01:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Wise Prince.</font>

28
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

29
00:01:49,260 --> 00:01:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was told that you wished 
to see me, Brother.</font>

30
00:01:52,890 --> 00:01:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

31
00:01:54,260 --> 00:01:56,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to ask your opinion.</font>

32
00:01:57,390 --> 00:01:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've received an imperial command</font>

33
00:01:59,730 --> 00:02:02,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to have Reiss here lead a force</font>

34
00:02:02,670 --> 00:02:05,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to suppress a rebellion 
at the southern border.</font>

35
00:02:06,200 --> 00:02:09,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If those barbarians are shown 
any compassion, they get cocky.</font>

36
00:02:09,840 --> 00:02:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we're to dispatch a regular army</font>

37
00:02:12,710 --> 00:02:15,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to show them how much 
greater our strength is.</font>

38
00:02:15,310 --> 00:02:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

39
00:02:17,530 --> 00:02:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Reiss Keiki, eh?</i></font>

40
00:02:18,740 --> 00:02:24,200
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#f9fbf6">Reiss Keiki 
<font size="13">Direct Subordinate of the Fourth Prince</font></font></b></font>

41
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:22,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aside from his many acts of valor,</i></font>

42
00:02:22,300 --> 00:02:24,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he's more than talented 
enough to lead an army.</i></font>

43
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even among all of my brother's 
knights, he is exceptional.</i></font>

44
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me just one thing.</font>

45
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:34,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. Please, ask me anything.</font>

46
00:02:35,350 --> 00:02:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many soldiers are there, <i>truly</i>?</font>

47
00:02:58,570 --> 00:03:00,570
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

48
00:02:58,570 --> 00:03:00,570
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#051529">m 0 0 l 235 0 l 225 8 l 235 15 l 18 15 l 30 8 l 18 0</font></font>

49
00:04:14,770 --> 00:04:15,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something wrong?</font>

50
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I asked you how many soldiers
you'll be leading.</font>

51
00:04:21,100 --> 00:04:23,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That is, um...</font>

52
00:04:24,380 --> 00:04:27,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean by "truly," Noah?</font>

53
00:04:29,490 --> 00:04:30,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Reiss!</font>

54
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:32,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you hiding?!</font>

55
00:04:35,230 --> 00:04:38,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Please forgive me.</font>

56
00:04:39,940 --> 00:04:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother, it's not a serious matter.</font>

57
00:04:43,930 --> 00:04:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But imperial forces receive funding
from the Ministry of Military Affairs</font>

58
00:04:48,250 --> 00:04:51,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">based on how many soldiers 
are registered, correct?</font>

59
00:04:51,550 --> 00:04:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

60
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:56,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's common for generals 
to register non-soldiers,</font>

61
00:04:56,170 --> 00:04:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">such as merchants and collaborators,</font>

62
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and keep the excess 
funding for themselves.</font>

63
00:05:02,870 --> 00:05:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sincerely apologize.</font>

64
00:05:04,570 --> 00:05:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, you...</font>

65
00:05:06,030 --> 00:05:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please wait a moment, Brother.</font>

66
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And Reiss, stop cowering.</font>

67
00:05:10,300 --> 00:05:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's within a general's authority 
to add new soldiers.</font>

68
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not trying to place blame.</font>

69
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normally, that would be fine.</font>

70
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Registering soldiers in name 
only can serve as a deterrent.</font>

71
00:05:22,990 --> 00:05:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

72
00:05:24,020 --> 00:05:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sometimes it's better to say</font>

73
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:29,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you have an army of 100,000, even 
if that isn't the actual number.</font>

74
00:05:29,990 --> 00:05:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Precisely.</font>

75
00:05:31,510 --> 00:05:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You understand these matters well.</font>

76
00:05:33,530 --> 00:05:34,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brilliant as always, Noah.</font>

77
00:05:35,640 --> 00:05:37,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this occasion is different.</font>

78
00:05:38,290 --> 00:05:41,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The emperor's order was 
for a sweeping victory.</font>

79
00:05:41,550 --> 00:05:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I asked about the 
extent of your embellishment.</font>

80
00:05:45,440 --> 00:05:46,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer me honestly.</font>

81
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Around two thousand, I believe.</font>

82
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then make sure you can 
actually supply that many.</font>

83
00:05:53,370 --> 00:05:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, Your Highness. At once.</font>

84
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I borrow a pen and paper?</font>

85
00:05:57,780 --> 00:05:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

86
00:06:03,300 --> 00:06:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take this to the Ministry 
of Military Affairs.</font>

87
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:11,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll supply enough to cover two
thousand more as miscellaneous expenses.</font>

88
00:06:11,310 --> 00:06:12,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The excess is yours.</font>

89
00:06:12,820 --> 00:06:14,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

90
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take it. And in return...</font>

91
00:06:17,550 --> 00:06:20,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will <i>not</i> tolerate defeat. Understand?</font>

92
00:06:21,200 --> 00:06:22,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, Your Highness!</font>

93
00:06:22,990 --> 00:06:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, well.</font>

94
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What masterful usage of 
the carrot and stick.</font>

95
00:06:35,210 --> 00:06:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Noah...</font>

96
00:06:37,330 --> 00:06:41,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you haven't experienced 
war yet, have you?</font>

97
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Correct.</font>

98
00:06:43,570 --> 00:06:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even at age twelve,</i></font>

99
