102
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:50,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the rule of the imperial family.</i></font>

103
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:53,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Many royal babies die prematurely,</i></font>

104
00:06:53,940 --> 00:06:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>meaning they don't survive 
long after birth.</i></font>

105
00:06:57,680 --> 00:07:00,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Officially, it's attributed 
to an epidemic,</i></font>

106
00:07:00,450 --> 00:07:03,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but most of them are identified 
as murder by poison</i></font>

107
00:07:03,140 --> 00:07:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>by those competing for more power.</i></font>

108
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Either way, a prince is 
a valuable living heir.</i></font>

109
00:07:09,540 --> 00:07:11,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They aren't permitted to go to battle</i></font>

110
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>until they've grown to adulthood, 
except by imperial order.</i></font>

111
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're twelve now.</font>

112
00:07:17,570 --> 00:07:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it look better if 
you got some experience now,</font>

113
00:07:20,340 --> 00:07:22,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">before you start ruling your fief?</font>

114
00:07:22,610 --> 00:07:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If the emperor orders me to 
go, I'll go at any time.</font>

115
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have a magic sword. I doubt 
you would have much difficulty.</font>

116
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:32,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When was your first campaign, Brother?</font>

117
00:07:33,100 --> 00:07:34,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, me? I—</font>

118
00:07:38,900 --> 00:07:40,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on?!</font>

119
00:07:40,150 --> 00:07:41,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please help me!</font>

120
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:47,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold up, damn it!</font>

121
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:48,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You stupid brats!</font>

122
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're nothing but trouble!</font>

123
00:07:51,180 --> 00:07:53,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's no use trying to run!</font>

124
00:07:53,300 --> 00:07:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone, please help!</font>

125
00:07:56,000 --> 00:07:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, come with me!</font>

126
00:07:57,570 --> 00:07:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No!</font>

127
00:07:58,850 --> 00:07:59,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Stop it.</font>

128
00:08:02,530 --> 00:08:03,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

129
00:08:03,440 --> 00:08:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little brat! Keep your nose 
in your own business!</font>

130
00:08:07,300 --> 00:08:08,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's your registration?</font>

131
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

132
00:08:09,410 --> 00:08:11,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's your registration? 
Your documents?</font>

133
00:08:11,760 --> 00:08:13,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is the name of your business?</font>

134
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer me.</font>

135
00:08:16,210 --> 00:08:19,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know that unregistered slave 
trading is a serious crime</font>

136
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">under imperial law, right?</font>

137
00:08:22,270 --> 00:08:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shut up, you stupid brat!</font>

138
00:08:24,660 --> 00:08:25,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get him!</font>

139
00:08:39,910 --> 00:08:41,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done.</font>

140
00:08:41,320 --> 00:08:42,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow...</font>

141
00:08:42,230 --> 00:08:43,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible!</font>

142
00:08:43,270 --> 00:08:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He handled himself like 
a real sword master!</font>

143
00:08:46,530 --> 00:08:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What household does he belong to?</font>

144
00:08:49,340 --> 00:08:50,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

145
00:08:51,750 --> 00:08:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes...</font>

146
00:08:53,710 --> 00:08:56,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These are underground
slave traders, yes?</font>

147
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They said... we'd be worth good money...</font>

148
00:09:04,930 --> 00:09:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough.</font>

149
00:09:08,910 --> 00:09:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a pleasure it is to 
meet you, Wise Prince.</font>

150
00:09:13,540 --> 00:09:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I make my living off of kids 
like the ones you see here.</font>

151
00:09:18,330 --> 00:09:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My name is...</font>

152
00:09:20,070 --> 00:09:22,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On second thought,
perhaps I shouldn't tell you.</font>

153
00:09:22,680 --> 00:09:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

154
00:09:23,580 --> 00:09:30,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I work for First Prince Gilbert.</font>

155
00:09:27,420 --> 00:09:30,540
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#efefeb">Gilbert Ararat 
<font size="13">First Prince</font></font></b></font>

156
00:09:30,540 --> 00:09:32,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The first prince?</font>

157
00:09:32,650 --> 00:09:33,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

158
00:09:34,130 --> 00:09:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not only does he know who I am,</i></font>

159
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but he's threatening me not to meddle 
because he has Gilbert's backing.</i></font>

160
00:09:48,160 --> 00:09:50,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want to make waves here.</font>

161
00:09:50,720 --> 00:09:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, just pretend you 
never saw any of this.</font>

162
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brother, do you know this man?</font>

163
00:09:57,250 --> 00:09:58,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

164
00:09:58,770 --> 00:10:00,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I don't.</font>

165
00:10:01,180 --> 00:10:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My brother Henry says 
he doesn't know you,</font>

166
00:10:04,610 --> 00:10:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">nor do I.</font>

167
00:10:06,080 --> 00:10:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But of course not.</font>

168
00:10:08,100 --> 00:10:10,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A man such as I would not—</font>

169
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear...</font>

170
00:10:19,310 --> 00:10:23,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The nerve of this scoundrel to falsely 
claim he serves the first prince.</font>

171
00:10:23,080 --> 00:10:27,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He may have fooled others, but my 
brother and I will not be fooled.</font>

172
00:10:27,300 --> 00:10:29,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? So he was a fake?</font>

173
00:10:29,850 --> 00:10:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And... who are those two, anyway?</font>

174
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:33,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know them.</font>

175
00:10:33,900 --> 00:10:38,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the songstress Alichey's patron,
the Wise Prince!</font>

176
00:10:38,130 --> 00:10:39,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So he's real?</font>

177
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the others are the fakes?</font>

178
00:10:42,990 --> 00:10:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apprehend these men and take them 
to the first prince's estate.</font>

179
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:53,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain that they are scoundrels who 
falsely claimed to work for Gilbert.</font>

180
00:10:53,480 --> 00:10:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At once.</font>

181
00:10:55,830 --> 00:10:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring the children to my mansion for now.</font>

182
00:10:58,370 --> 00:11:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll hear their stories later.</font>

183
00:11:01,490 --> 00:11:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well done, Noah.</font>

184
00:11:03,370 --> 00:11:04,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You handled that brilliantly.</font>

185
00:11:04,850 --> 00:11:07,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad it all worked out.</font>

186
00:11:07,720 --> 00:11:12,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they did work for Gilbert,
I couldn't kill them.</font>

187
00:11:12,740 --> 00:11:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I'd left them 
to their own devices,</font>

188
00:11:15,510 --> 00:11:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the people would think I allowed 
underground slave trading to happen.</font>

189
00:11:19,830 --> 00:11:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's best if I made them out to be fakes,</font>

190
00:11:21,910 --> 00:11:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and let Gilbert handle them himself.</font>

191
00:11:27,720 --> 00:11:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way you do things always 
surprises and amazes me.</font>

192
00:11:42,240 --> 00:11:43,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness.</font>

193
00:11:45,290 --> 00:11:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

194
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it, Noah?</font>

195
00:11:50,790 --> 00:11:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A messenger of
First Prince Gilbert was here.</font>

196
00:11:54,830 --> 00:11:57,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What did he say?</font>

197
00:11:57,470 --> 00:11:59,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Thank you for catching them.</font>

198
00:11:59,950 --> 00:12:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I interrogated the slave traders,</font>

199
00:12:02,130 --> 00:12:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they were indeed falsely claiming 
my name to run their business.</font>

200
00:12:05,450 --> 00:12:08,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I intended to send them to 
court as soon as tomorrow...</font>

201
00:12:09,830 --> 00:12:13,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but they committed suicide 
while my back was turned."</font>

202
00:12:13,950 --> 00:12:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

203
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Honestly...</i></font>

204
00:12:17,520 --> 00:12:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And people are supposed 
to be treasures...</i></font>

205
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:24,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These words must have crossed 
my brother's mind as well:</i></font>

206
00:12:24,630 --> 00:12:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"The lizard has shed its tail."</i></font>

207
00:12:27,560 --> 00:12:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gilbert ordered those men to run the 
underground slave trade, didn't he?</font>

208
00:12:32,190 --> 00:12:33,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

209
00:12:33,270 --> 00:12:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has absorbed himself in acquiring 
shops, buying private estates,</font>

210
00:12:36,700 --> 00:12:39,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and senseless activities 
like that for a long time.</font>

211
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:41,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't blame him.</font>

212
00:12:41,050 --> 00:12:41,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why not?</font>

213
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:46,490
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="13"><font color="#4d493a">Fourteenth Prince 
Gary</font></font></b></font></font>

214
00:12:42,070 --> 00:12:49,700
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="13"><font color="#4d493a">Fourth Prince 
Henry</font></font></b></font></font>

215
00:12:42,610 --> 00:12:49,700
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="13"><font color="#4d493a">Third Prince 
Kilo</font></font></b></font></font>

216
00:12:42,980 --> 00:12:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gilbert may be the first prince, 
but he's a concubine's son.</font>

217
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:49,700
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="13"><font color="#4d493a">Crown Prince, Second Prince 
Albert</font></font></b></font></font>

218
00:12:47,330 --> 00:12:48,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He can't succeed the throne.</font>

219
00:12:47,620 --> 00:12:49,700
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="13"><font color="#4d493a">First Prince 
Gilbert</font></font></b></font></font>

220
00:12:49,700 --> 00:12:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps, to vent his frustration,</font>

221
00:12:52,060 --> 00:12:55,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he's looking for something he can 
do without succeeding the throne.</font>

222
00:12:55,270 --> 00:12:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The slave trade and
private estates are just proxies.</font>

223
00:12:59,780 --> 00:13:02,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You even know that?</font>

224
00:13:02,530 --> 00:13:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never cease to amaze me.</font>

225
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyone could figure it out 
with a bit of thought.</font>

226
00:13:09,830 --> 00:13:11,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not exactly.</font>

227
00:13:12,810 --> 00:13:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This whole thing nauseated me,</font>

228
00:13:15,690 --> 00:13:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I feel a bit better now.</font>

229
00:13:19,110 --> 00:13:23,980
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Episode 6</font></b></font></font>

230
00:13:19,110 --> 00:13:23,980
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Dark Clouds</font></b></font></font>

231
00:13:26,510 --> 00:13:27,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've pulled some strings.</font>

232
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:31,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">None of you will ever be sold.</font>

233
00:13:33,170 --> 00:13:35,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all free now.</font>

234
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is this what I think it is?</i></font>

235
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have anywhere to go?</font>

236
00:13:41,650 --> 00:13:43,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

237
00:13:43,080 --> 00:13:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was sold in exchange for money 
to buy this year's seed rice.</font>

238
00:13:48,250 --> 00:13:50,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was sold to pay for 
my mother's funeral.</font>

239
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:52,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One less mouth to feed.</font>

240
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dad really likes to gamble.</font>

241
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As I suspected.
They have no home to return to.</i></font>

242
00:13:57,280 --> 00:14:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And with parents like that, if they did 
go home, they'd just be sold again.</i></font>

243
00:14:01,540 --> 00:14:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dylan.</font>

244
00:14:02,730 --> 00:14:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

245
00:14:03,720 --> 00:14:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take them in.</font>

246
00:14:06,650 --> 00:14:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Find them jobs and places to sleep 
wherever available.</font>

247
00:14:09,480 --> 00:14:13,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if any wish to study, 
help them do it.</font>

248
00:14:13,700 --> 00:14:16,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood. As always, eh?</font>

249
00:14:17,060 --> 00:14:21,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're going to buy us?</font>

250
00:14:22,430 --> 00:14:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not buying you.</font>

251
00:14:24,430 --> 00:14:28,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you want to leave,
you're free to do so at any time.</font>

252
00:14:29,130 --> 00:14:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the one thing I won't 
tolerate is betrayal.</font>

253
00:14:36,380 --> 00:14:38,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is that too difficult for them?</i></font>

254
00:14:38,480 --> 00:14:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Be grateful for His Highness's
kindness and do the best you can.</font>

255
00:14:44,020 --> 00:14:45,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank him, quickly.</font>

256
00:14:45,830 --> 00:14:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank you.</font>

257
00:14:46,560 --> 00:14:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thank you.</font>

258
00:14:51,630 --> 00:14:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>People are treasures, eh?</i></font>

259
00:14:57,090 --> 00:14:58,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that's right!</font>

260
00:15:03,780 --> 00:15:06,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You called, Master?</font>

261
00:15:06,930 --> 00:15:11,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of your birthday gifts have 
been handled without incident—</font>

262
00:15:11,740 --> 00:15:12,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need to report that.</font>

263
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is already apparent.</font>

264
00:15:18,090 --> 00:15:21,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evelyn, I brought this for you.</font>

265
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

266
00:15:24,290 --> 00:15:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your dismissal.</font>

267
00:15:26,030 --> 00:15:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to be the administrator 
of a small region within Almeria.</font>

268
00:15:29,460 --> 00:15:30,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Administrator?</font>

269
00:15:31,240 --> 00:15:35,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Now you're also a proper 
government official.</font>

270
00:15:35,070 --> 00:15:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But I...</font>

271
00:15:37,580 --> 00:15:42,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>An administrator is a key office,
also popularly known as a magistrate.</i></font>

272
00:15:42,180 --> 00:15:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a major promotion for a maid.</i></font>

273
00:15:46,040 --> 00:15:50,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The fief that the prince received 
from the emperor is vast.</i></font>

274
00:15:50,060 --> 00:15:53,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It would be impossible for him 
to rule over it all himself.</i></font>

275
00:15:53,900 --> 00:15:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So he has assigned administrators to 
various regions to act as his proxies.</i></font>

276
00:16:00,520 --> 00:16:05,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been watching you for many years, 
and you're the most clever of my maids.</font>

277
00:16:05,970 --> 00:16:11,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I felt that just taking care of guests at 
this mansion is a waste of your talents.</font>

278
00:16:11,230 --> 00:16:15,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But... that is... I...</font>

279
00:16:15,470 --> 00:16:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I would rather keep working for you</font>

280
00:16:20,050 --> 00:16:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">than go out there and 
move up in the world!</font>

281
00:16:22,720 --> 00:16:24,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

282
00:16:24,980 --> 00:16:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you can, and will, grow.</font>

283
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:31,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'll work for me as an administrator,
it will be known that I,</font>

284
00:16:31,300 --> 00:16:33,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the one who appointed you,
am an excellent judge of people.</font>

285
00:16:35,220 --> 00:16:36,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Evelyn.</font>

286
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave this mansion and work for me.</font>

287
00:16:41,230 --> 00:16:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For... you...</font>

288
00:16:48,820 --> 00:16:51,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-All right! I understand!</font>

289
00:16:52,030 --> 00:16:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good.</font>

290
00:16:58,210 --> 00:16:59,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Amazing.</font>

291
00:16:59,610 --> 00:17:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is?</font>

292
00:17:00,650 --> 00:17:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's obvious!</font>

293
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The way you put people to use is 
nothing like how the first prince—</font>

294
00:17:05,890 --> 00:17:06,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shirley.</font>

295
00:17:07,290 --> 00:17:09,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is not something you 
should say aloud.</font>

296
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right. I apologize.</font>

297
00:17:19,060 --> 00:17:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

298
00:17:20,560 --> 00:17:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he really is amazing.</font>

299
00:17:24,970 --> 00:17:27,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've heard the story, Noah.</font>

300
00:17:28,050 --> 00:17:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You managed to defend Gilbert's honor.</font>

301
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was coincidental.</font>

302
00:17:34,290 --> 00:17:37,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I merely captured people 
who were breaking the law.</font>

303
00:17:37,110 --> 00:17:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So my brother reported it himself.</i></font>

304
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Smart.</i></font>

305
00:17:41,130 --> 00:17:45,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Instead of keeping secrets, he's made 
it appear as if his hands are clean.</i></font>

306
00:17:46,080 --> 00:17:49,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still, to think such 
scoundrels were out there.</font>

307
00:17:49,580 --> 00:17:53,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What sort of crime is underground 
slave trading, again?</font>

308
00:17:53,090 --> 00:17:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In cases of unregistered slave trading,</font>

309
00:17:55,280 --> 00:17:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the ringleader's dominant 
arm is to be severed,</font>

310
00:17:57,560 --> 00:18:00,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and any others involved are 
drafted into military service.</font>

311
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that correct, First Prime Minister?</font>

312
00:18:04,630 --> 00:18:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is precisely as His Highness says.</font>

313
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. Were you hurt in any way?</font>

314
00:18:12,680 --> 00:18:16,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear the criminals flew into 
a rage and attacked you.</font>

315
00:18:16,470 --> 00:18:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thankfully, I was able to 
turn the tables on them.</font>

316
00:18:19,370 --> 00:18:22,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose, since it's you, 
I didn't even need to ask.</font>

317
00:18:22,480 --> 00:18:24,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Had it been me,</font>

318
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:28,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would have been undercover, 
so I may have been defeated</font>

319
00:18:28,280 --> 00:18:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while debating whether 
to reveal my identity.</font>

320
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That would amount to a crime 
against the imperial family,</font>

321
00:18:34,430 --> 00:18:36,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">punishable by death.</font>

322
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

323
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:46,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Under imperial law, if the criminal does 
not know His Majesty's identity—</font>

324
00:18:46,030 --> 00:18:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in other words, if he is undercover 
and has not yet named himself—</font>

325
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there is no crime against 
the imperial family.</font>

326
00:18:52,570 --> 00:18:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is treated merely as assault.</font>

327
00:18:57,230 --> 00:18:58,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did I go too far?</i></font>

328
00:18:59,630 --> 00:19:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is or isn't considered rude to say 
to the emperor is a delicate matter.</i></font>

329
00:19:05,050 --> 00:19:07,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If he was merely being hypothetical,</i></font>

330
00:19:07,510 --> 00:19:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>perhaps I shouldn't have 
pointed out his mistake.</i></font>

331
00:19:10,420 --> 00:19:12,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's always best to speak the truth,</i></font>

332
00:19:13,310 --> 00:19:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but not when it makes a 
prime minister look bad.</i></font>

333
00:19:16,880 --> 00:19:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Should I apologize?</i></font>

334
00:19:22,620 --> 00:19:26,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I'd say I won that bet.</font>

335
00:19:26,110 --> 00:19:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I underestimated him.</font>

336
00:19:29,130 --> 00:19:32,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... what does that mean?</font>

337
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:37,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I just had a little bet going 
with the first prime minister.</font>

338
00:19:37,090 --> 00:19:41,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a test to see whether or 
not you could describe the law.</font>

339
00:19:41,340 --> 00:19:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh...</font>

340
00:19:42,860 --> 00:19:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A test? But why?</i></font>

341
00:19:45,820 --> 00:19:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have always known that you were strict 
