342
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was testing that, just to make sure.</font>

343
00:19:54,710 --> 00:19:56,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah...</font>

344
00:19:57,600 --> 00:20:00,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In the name of the Emperor,</font>

345
00:20:00,730 --> 00:20:04,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hereby appoint Noah Ararat 
