348
00:20:12,710 --> 00:20:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Long live Noah,
Minister-Prince of Justice! Banzai!</font>

349
00:20:16,130 --> 00:20:23,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Banzai! Banzai! Banzai! Banzai!</font>

350
00:20:32,020 --> 00:20:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All I did was answer the way I always do,</i></font>

351
00:20:35,300 --> 00:20:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and I was made minister of justice.</i></font>

352
00:20:41,250 --> 00:20:43,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Am I making too much of this?</i></font>

353
00:20:43,750 --> 00:20:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or was there something else 
behind this decision?</i></font>

354
00:20:52,540 --> 00:20:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can see why she's the most popular 
songstress in the empire right now.</font>

355
00:20:55,860 --> 00:20:57,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a beautiful voice.</font>

356
00:20:57,780 --> 00:20:59,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like my heart is being cleansed.</font>

357
00:21:02,450 --> 00:21:05,770
