358
00:21:15,550 --> 00:21:17,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so good!</font>

359
00:21:50,210 --> 00:21:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty, it seems the 
report was indeed true.</font>

360
00:21:56,370 --> 00:21:57,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

361
00:21:59,110 --> 00:22:00,940
